<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>黃俞蓁 | 個人簡介</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #2c3e50;
            --accent-color: #3498db;
            --bg-color: #f4f7f6;
            --text-color: #333;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif, "Microsoft JhengHei";
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        hr {
            border: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: #eee;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        .section {
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .section h3 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-color);
            padding-left: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .info-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .info-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .info-list b {
            width: 100px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .email-link {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .email-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #888;
        }

        /* 簡單的標籤樣式 */
        .tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e1f0fa;
            color: #3498db;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-right: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <h1>黃俞蓁</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">國立金門大學 資訊工程學系 | 學生</div>
    </header>

    <hr>

    <div class="section">
        <h3>關於我</h3>
        <ul class="info-list">
            <li><b>就讀學校：</b>國立金門大學</li>
            <li><b>電子郵件：</b><a class="email-link" href="mailto:s111410548@stu.nqu.edu.tw">s111410548@stu.nqu.edu.tw</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h3>興趣愛好</h3>
        <span class="tag">📖 看書</span>
        <span class="tag">🎮 打電動</span>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h3>未來期許</h3>
        <p>深耕資工專業知識，精進程式開發技能，期許未來能畢業後順利進入產業，<b>成為一名優秀的工程師</b>。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        © 2026 Powered by Yu-Zhen Huang
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
